      ******************************************************************        
      * BUSINESS OBJECTS REPORT REQUEST COPYBOOK.                               
      *                                                                         
      * !! ENSURE THAT ANY CHANGES MADE TO THIS COPYBOOK ARE MADE IN            
      *    BOTH 01 LEVELS TO KEEP THEM IN SYNC WITH EACH OTHER.                 
      *    THE 01 LEVELS ARE USED FOR MAPPING COPYBOOK FIELDS TO                
      *    XML TAGS, SO THEY NEED TO MATCH !!                                   
      ******************************************************************        
                                                                                
       01  IS010-REPORT-REQUEST.                                                
           05  IS010-REQUEST-ID              PIC X(48) VALUE SPACES.            
           05  IS010-REPORT-NAME             PIC X(50) VALUE SPACES.            
           05  IS010-REPORT-FOLDER           PIC X(150) VALUE SPACES.           
           05  IS010-OUTPUT-FORMAT           PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.            
           05  IS010-DESTINATION-TYPE        PIC X(15) VALUE SPACES.            
           05  IS010-DESTINATION-PATH        PIC X(225) VALUE SPACES.           
           05  IS010-DESTINATION-FILENAME    PIC X(50) VALUE SPACES.            
      * Default value for expiry time is 5 minutes.                             
      * Set to -1 for an unlimited expiry time. That would mean that            
      *    the report request would remain even after the requesting            
      *    application has given up on waiting for a schedule response.         
      * Expiry is in tenths of seconds.                                         
           05  IS010-REQUEST-EXPIRY-TIME     PIC S9(09)                         
                                             VALUE +3000                        
                                             SIGN LEADING SEPARATE.             
           05  IS010-PARM-DELIMITER          PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.            
           05  IS010-NUM-OF-PARAMS           PIC 9(02).                         
           05  IS010-PARAMETERS-TABLE.                                          
               10  IS010-PARAMETERS          PIC X(500)                         
                                      OCCURS 0 TO 15 TIMES                      
                                      DEPENDING ON IS010-NUM-OF-PARAMS.         
           05  FILLER                        PIC X(100).                        
                                                                                
      *01  reportRequest REDEFINES IS010-REPORT-REQUEST.                        
       01  reportRequest.                                                       
           05  uniqueRequestId                PIC X(48).                        
           05  reportTitle                    PIC X(50).                        
           05  folderPath                     PIC X(150).                       
           05  outputFormat                   PIC X(15).                        
           05  destinationType                PIC X(15).                        
           05  destinationPath                PIC X(225).                       
           05  destinationFileName            PIC X(50).                        
           05  filler                         PIC X(10).                        
           05  parmDelimiter                  PIC X(01).                        
           05  numberParameters               PIC 9(02).                        
           05  parameterList.                                                   
               10  reportParam                PIC X(500)                        
                                      OCCURS 0 TO 15 TIMES                      
                                      DEPENDING ON numberParameters             
                                      VALUE SPACES.                             
           05  filler                         PIC X(100).                       
